==Etymology==
Neo-Latin formation, from combining form '''[[americ-]]''', ''America'', + suffix '''[[-ium]]'''.  '''America''' is a Latin variation of the first name of '''[[Amerigo Vespucci]]''', an Italian mapmaker.

